---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'healthcare-system', text: 'Healthcare System', level: 2 },
  { id: 'visa-requirements', text: 'Visa Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'insurance-requirements', text: 'Insurance Requirements', level: 2 },
  { id: 'recommended-providers', text: 'Recommended Providers', level: 2 },
  { id: 'costs', text: 'Expected Costs', level: 2 },
  { id: 'scenarios', text: 'Real-World Scenarios', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'Common Questions', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'PNG Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/papua-new-guinea/insurance' },
  { title: 'Insurance for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors' },
  { title: 'Australia for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/australia' },
  { title: 'Fiji for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/fiji' },
  { title: 'Indonesia for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/indonesia' },
];

const providerColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'entryAge', header: 'Max Entry Age' },
  { key: 'renewal', header: 'Renewal' },
  { key: 'monthlyFrom', header: 'From (65-69)' },
  { key: 'pngFit', header: 'PNG Fit' },
];

const providerRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'PGK$1,755-2,510/mo', pngFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'BUPA Global', entryAge: '79', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'PGK$2,050-2,930/mo', pngFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'PGK$1,580-2,260/mo', pngFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'Pacific International', entryAge: '70', renewal: 'Varies', monthlyFrom: 'PGK$1,200-1,800/mo', pngFit: 'Regional' },
];

const costColumns = [
  { key: 'category', header: 'Expense' },
  { key: 'monthly', header: 'Monthly' },
  { key: 'annual', header: 'Annual' },
];

const costRows = [
  { category: 'International Insurance (65-69)', monthly: 'PGK$1,580-2,510', annual: 'PGK$18,960-30,120' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (70-74)', monthly: 'PGK$2,165-3,350', annual: 'PGK$25,980-40,200' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (75-79)', monthly: 'PGK$2,910-4,490', annual: 'PGK$34,920-53,880' },
  { category: 'Private Clinic (Port Moresby)', monthly: 'PGK$200-500/visit', annual: 'As needed' },
  { category: 'Evacuation to Australia', monthly: 'N/A', annual: 'PGK$100K-300K' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Health Insurance for Seniors in Papua New Guinea 2026 | Retirement Guide"
  description="Guide to health insurance for seniors in Papua New Guinea. Tribal cultures, biodiversity, security concerns, and coverage for adventurous visitors 65+."
  headline="Health Insurance for Seniors in Papua New Guinea"
  subheadline="Papua New Guinea offers extraordinary tribal cultures, incredible biodiversity, WWII history, and raw frontier adventure—but significant security and healthcare challenges make it unsuitable for typical retirement."
  heroImage="/images/countries/papua-new-guinea-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Senior Plans →"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Critical: PNG Is Challenging</h2>
  <p>
    Papua New Guinea presents significant challenges: serious security concerns (high crime, including violent crime), very limited healthcare, undeveloped infrastructure, and difficult logistics. While offering extraordinary cultural and natural experiences, PNG is NOT recommended for typical senior retirement. Only for organized tours or those with strong professional reasons.
  </p>

  <p>
    Port Moresby is capital with most services and highest crime. Highlands offer tribal culture. Islands have diving. Population ~9 million. Cairns, Australia (1.5-hour flight) provides essential medical backup. Security is primary concern.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-900 mb-3">Critical Security Warning</h3>
    <ul class="text-red-800 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Crime:</strong> High violent crime including carjacking, armed robbery</li>
      <li><strong>Port Moresby:</strong> Particularly dangerous; walking not recommended</li>
      <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Very limited; evacuation essential</li>
      <li><strong>Infrastructure:</strong> Roads poor; internal flights unreliable</li>
      <li><strong>Recommendation:</strong> NOT suitable for independent senior travel</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="healthcare-system">PNG Healthcare System</h2>
  <p>
    PNG healthcare is very limited—Pacific International Hospital (Port Moresby) is best private option but limited specialists. Public hospitals basic with shortages. Highlands and islands have minimal care. Complex cases require evacuation to Cairns, Australia (1.5 hours) with excellent hospitals.
  </p>

  <p>
    Cairns is essential backup—Cairns Hospital and private options provide Australian-standard care. International insurance with Australia evacuation coverage absolutely essential. Don't underestimate healthcare limitations.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-2">Australia Evacuation Essential</h3>
    <p class="text-amber-800 mb-0">
      Cairns is 1.5 hours away with Australian healthcare. Brisbane 3 hours for complex cases. PNG cannot treat most serious conditions. Insurance with Australia coverage is absolutely non-negotiable. Consider helicopter evacuation for remote areas.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="visa-requirements">Visa Options</h2>
  <p>
    PNG visa options (if visiting):
  </p>

  <h3>Tourist Visa</h3>
  <p>
    60-day visa available. Some nationalities get visa on arrival.
  </p>

  <h3>Business Visa</h3>
  <p>
    For business purposes. Various categories.
  </p>

  <h3>Work Permit</h3>
  <p>
    For those working in PNG. Mining/resources sector most common.
  </p>

  <h3>Retirement</h3>
  <p>
    No formal retirement program. Very few Westerners retire to PNG. Security and healthcare make it impractical.
  </p>

  <h2 id="insurance-requirements">Insurance Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance requirements for PNG:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Entry:</strong> Travel insurance strongly recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Coverage:</strong> Comprehensive international coverage essential</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Australia coverage absolutely critical</li>
    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Consider evacuation for security situations</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for PNG</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
      Maximum coverage required—comprehensive international insurance with strong Australia evacuation. Consider security evacuation coverage. Local care handles only basic needs. Premium providers essential for challenging destination.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="recommended-providers">Recommended Insurance Providers</h2>
  <p>
    For any PNG visit, comprehensive evacuation coverage essential:
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={providerColumns} rows={providerRows} />

  <h3>Critical Considerations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cigna Global:</strong> Strong Asia-Pacific network, Australia access</li>
    <li><strong>BUPA Global:</strong> Highest entry age (79), comprehensive</li>
    <li><strong>Australia access:</strong> Cairns is lifeline</li>
    <li><strong>Security coverage:</strong> Consider evacuation for unrest</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Consider Safer Alternatives</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Similar Pacific experiences with better safety and healthcare.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/insurance-for/seniors/in/fiji" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Fiji Guide</a>
      <a href="/insurance-for/seniors/in/australia" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Australia Guide</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="costs">Expected Insurance Costs</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance costs for PNG (PGK ~3.9 to USD):
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

  <h3>Cost Considerations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Premium destination:</strong> High-risk location means higher premiums</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation focus:</strong> Australia evacuation critical</li>
    <li><strong>Security costs:</strong> Compound living, security guards add expense</li>
    <li><strong>Don't economize:</strong> This is not place to cut insurance corners</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="scenarios">Real-World Scenarios</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 1: Organized Dive Tour, 66</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> 2-week liveaboard dive trip. Organized tour with security.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with diving and evacuation coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$600/month. Managed experience; comprehensive backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 2: WWII History Tour, 68</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> Organized Kokoda Track tour. Group with security.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> BUPA Global with trekking coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$700/month. Historical significance; premium protection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 3: NOT Recommended</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> Independent senior retirement in PNG.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Choose Fiji, Australia, or other Pacific alternative.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Reality:</strong> Security and healthcare make PNG unsuitable for senior retirement.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Can seniors retire to PNG?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Not recommended—high crime, very limited healthcare, undeveloped infrastructure. Few Westerners retire to PNG. Those living there typically work in mining/resources with company security and evacuation support.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">How bad is the security situation?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Serious—Port Moresby ranks among world's most dangerous cities. Armed robbery, carjacking, assault common. Walking not recommended. Compound living with security standard for expats. Highlands have tribal violence. Islands generally safer.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is any PNG travel possible for seniors?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Yes with organized tours—reputable tour operators provide security, logistics, and emergency support. Liveaboard dive trips, organized cultural tours, and Kokoda Track treks with guides can be done safely. Independent travel not recommended.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What makes PNG special despite challenges?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Extraordinary—800+ languages, incredible tribal diversity, pristine coral reefs, rare wildlife (birds of paradise), WWII history. One of last true frontiers. Amazing for those who can manage the challenges safely.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">If Visiting PNG</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Get comprehensive coverage with Australia evacuation.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/bupa-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get BUPA Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Papua New Guinea presents significant security and healthcare challenges. NOT recommended for senior retirement. Organized tours only. This guide is for informational purposes. Always check current travel advisories.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
